ect/blogs/facebook-applications-accidentally-leaking-access-third-parties\"><span class=\"RefSource\"><span class=\"EmphasisFontCategoryNonProportional \">http://www.symantec.com/connect/blogs/facebook-applications-accidentally-leaking-access-third-parties</span></span></a></span> (June 26, 2013)<span class=\"Occurrences\"></span></div></li></ol></div></section><section class=\"Section1 RenderAsSection1\"><h2 class=\"Heading\" id=\"copyrightInformation\">Copyright information</h2><div class=\"ArticleCopyright content\"><div class=\"ChapterCopyright\">\u00a9\u00a0Springer International Publishing Switzerland\u00a02013</div></div></section><section id=\"authorsandaffiliations\" class=\"Section1 RenderAsSection1\"><h2 class=\"Heading\">Authors and Affiliations</h2><div class=\"content authors-affiliations u-interface\"><ul class=\"test-contributor-names\"><li itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" class=\"u-mb-2 u-pt-4 u-pb-4\" itemprop=\"author\"><span itemprop=\"name\" class=\"authors-affiliations__name\">Konstantinos\u00a0Chronopoulos</span><ul class=\"authors-affiliations__indexes u-inline-list\" data-role=\"AuthorsIndexes\"><li data-affiliation=\"affiliation-1\">1</li></ul></li><li itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" class=\"u-mb-2 u-pt-4 u-pb-4\" itemprop=\"author\"><span itemprop=\"name\" class=\"authors-affiliations__name\">Maria\u00a0Gouseti</span><ul class=\"authors-affiliations__indexes u-inline-list\" data-role=\"AuthorsIndexes\"><li data-affiliation=\"affiliation-1\">1</li></ul></li><li itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" class=\"u-mb-2 u-pt-4 u-pb-4\" itemprop=\"author\"><span itemprop=\"name\" class=\"authors-affiliations__name\">Aggelos\u00a0Kiayias</span><ul class=\"authors-affiliations__indexes u-inline-list\" data-role=\"AuthorsIndexes\"><li data-affiliation=\"affiliation-2\">2</li></ul></li></ul><ol class=\"test-affiliations\"><li class=\"affiliation\" data-test=\"affiliation-1\" data-affiliation-highl